					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Julian Sancton</h4>
												<p>Julian Sancton is a senior features editor at <em>Departures</em> magazine, where he writes about culture and travel. His work has appeared in <em>Vanity Fair</em>, <em>Esquire</em>, <em>The New Yorker</em>, <em>Wired</em>, and <em>Playboy</em>, among other publications. He has reported from every continent, including Antarctica, which he first visited while researching this book.</p>
